definitions.definition: A large brass musical instrument , usually in the bass range, played through a vibration of the lips upon the mouthpiece and fingering of the keys.
A large reed stop in organs .

main_definition: A large brass musical instrument , usually in the bass range, played through a vibration of the lips upon the mouthpiece and fingering of the keys.
secondary_definitions: A large reed stop in organs .

definitions.definition: ( anatomy ) A tube or tubular organ .
A type of Roman military trumpet , distinct from the modern tuba.

main_definition: ( anatomy ) A tube or tubular organ .
secondary_definitions: A type of Roman military trumpet , distinct from the modern tuba.
